headline: Sony hikes PlayStation 5 prices in US as tariff uncertainty weighs
summary: All three PlayStation 5 consoles will see a similar price hike, with the most expensive PS5 Pro version expected to cost $749.99, the company said in a blog post on Wednesday.  The price changes come after U.S. President Donald Trump announced sweeping tariffs on imports from global manufacturing hubs such as China and Japan, leading to fears of supply chain disruptions and high material costs.  Sony had raised prices of its consoles in various European markets in April.
